ThoughtFarmer,is,a,social,intranet,provider,A,social,intranet,is,an,internal,website,where,all,the,employees,of,a,given,company,can,author,content,and,connect,with,each,other,In,this,way,ThoughtFarmer,creates,a,simple,yet,powerful,platform,for,employee,communication,and,collaboration,ThoughtFarmer,provides,a,RESTful,API,that,allows,developers,to,integrate,functions,for,adding,altering,or,retrieving,information,from,a,ThoughtFarmer,intranet,with,another,website,or,application